    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-02-04T09:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-02-04T09:00:00-05:00" n="903"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d903">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/8739</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_PWH1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Page</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-02-04T14:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 4, 1918, 2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 5.10 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>8493. Your 6310, January 21, and my 8390, January 24. Mr. <persName
                        corresp="#p_BAJ1">Balfour</persName> has shown me the declaration upholding
                    independence and integrity of Persia, made by British and French Governments,
                    and submitted for participation of our Government through British Ambassador at
                    Washington. This he thinks is all that can be done at present.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PWH1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Page</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
